# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used with a windows machine or other OS, lock file might cause issues.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock contains exact versions, but can be committed.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock contains exact versions, but can be committed.
